  </li>
  <li>
    <p><strong>Make an <u>ObjectInputStream</u></strong></p>

    <p><img src="../../assets/img/image-20210415174609292.png" alt="image-20210415174609292" /></p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><strong><u>read</u> the objects</strong></p>

